*          APPEND VALUE #( %key = |{ ls_validmaterial-requestno }{ ls_validmaterial-requestitem }| ) TO ct_failed-requestitem.
*          APPEND VALUE #( %key = |{ ls_validmaterial-requestno }{ ls_validmaterial-requestitem }|
